Write a gtest that: (1) creates MetadataStorageFromDisk with persist_removal_queue=true and compaction_threshold=2, (2) submits 3 blobs via commit, (3) calls recordAsRemoved for 2 blobs (triggers compaction), (4) creates a new MetadataStorageFromDisk instance loading the same log file, (5) verifies the reloaded queue has exactly 1 blob (the one not removed), not 3. Currently it will have 3 (all original blobs re-loaded as ADD entries).
